  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the robata-grill to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Crush the graham crackers and mix with 1 tablespoon of unsalted butter until well combined.",
    "Press the crumb mixture into the bottom of a 9-inch kadhai. ",
    "Pour the heavy cream into a medium saucepan and heat it over medium heat until it starts to simmer.",
    "Remove the cream from heat and stir in the smoked pimenton, black truffle honey, cocoa powder, fleur de sel, smoked paprika, and unsalted butter until well combined.",
    "Fold in the carration ice cream until fully incorporated.",
    "Pour the ice cream mixture into the prepared kadhai and smooth the top.",
    "Bake for 30 minutes or until the top is caramelized and golden brown.",
    "Garnish with fresh thyme and serve warm."
  ],
